      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently requires significant mechanical work to be roadworthy, and there are visible signs of structural rust along the undercarriage and wheel wells. The interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. The exterior paint is heavily oxidized with several large dents and scratches throughout. It is being sold as-is.",
