    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this stunning vehicle that is in absolute mint condition! It looks and feels as if it just left the showroom floor, with a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that still smells new. Every detail has been meticulously cared for, making this the perfect choice for someone seeking a top-tier, like-new driving experience.",
