    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic and minor mechanical character. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few small stains, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need a suspension tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car for someone looking for transportation at an affordable price point.",
